<TITLE> Father of bdnews24.com journalist dies at 78 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, April 20 (bdnews24.com)  Robiul Karim, father of bdnews24.com correspondent Mohsinul Karim, died from old-age complications at his Nilphamari home Saturday at the age of 78. bdnews24.com journalists and others, saddened by the death of Karim, expressed condolences to the bereaved family. Karim was buried at the family graveyard in Chhatnai village of the district. Dhaka Reporters Unity president Alamgir Hossain and general secretary Illias Khan have expressed sorrows at the death of the father of the DRU's former office secretary, the journalists' organisation said in a statement Sunday. bd
